summary: AN ORDINANCE granting an easement for an access road over the City of Seattle, City Light Department's Skagit Transmission Line fee-owned Right-of-Way in Government Lot 12, of Section 6, Township 35 North, Range 11 East, W.M., Skagit County, Washington, and consenting to the continuation of the access road over the City's adjoining easement Right-of-Way (P.M. \#351106-3-301).
